{"tid":795744,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇邊個角色打得贏佢?","createTime":"2018-08-27T08:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T03:24:36.000Z","uid":8307,"like":7,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ba623405df90838ea37fdfe9655c6de0ae49451b","tid":795744,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T08:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/164150_4263f585b9ebb0a93277b84722477668.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F164150_4263f585b9ebb0a93277b84722477668.jpg&h=01193f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本部以藏<br />\n精通古兵法百般武藝<br />\n實戰專家,世界第一兵都係佢徒弟<br />\n二天一流創始人劍聖宮本武藏先生都打輸比佢<br />\n一擊秒殺美利堅合眾國都恐懼既人個仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/164453_9c7a47dfd66c1cdd1889fb34b24e5f66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F164453_9c7a47dfd66c1cdd1889fb34b24e5f66.jpg&h=bed5da89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我是旦例幾個出名最勁既例子出黎<br />\n龍珠個悟空都冇可能贏佢<br />\n因為本部以藏既氣同普通人冇分別<br />\n悟空根本冇可能察覺到佢,悟空同芝芝行緊公園個陣就比佢暗殺左<br />\n你可能話悟空刀槍不入,有咩可能比普通人殺死<br />\n但係根據復活的F入面悟空都係怕激光槍<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/164800_53189e00fb82af1d6135b8ac248bd3e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F164800_53189e00fb82af1d6135b8ac248bd3e7.jpg&h=5fff39b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一拳超人<br />\n一拳超人唔會同普通人認真打交<br />\n最多都係不敗,都係打唔贏本部以藏<br />\n<br />\nDIO<br />\n<img src=\"https://pa1.narvii.com/5818/719ce7262878be5e31a152f91258a0d1505bd571_hq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpa1.narvii.com%2F5818%2F719ce7262878be5e31a152f91258a0d1505bd571_hq.gif&h=70ca933e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n時間暫停既替身<br />\n因為本部以藏既精通古兵法同百般武藝<br />\n所以識得用波紋氣功都好合理<br />\n只要學2jo係dio發動the world之前將啲波紋隱藏係身入面,dio就會輸<br />\n因為本部係實戰高手,所以唔會好似2jo咁比dio發現左呢招古惑招<br />\n<br />\n一方通行<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/5-30-2015/LA2T4S.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F5-30-2015%2FLA2T4S.gif&h=9a0dddff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為本部精通百般武藝同古兵法,所以識用木原神拳都好合理<br />\n<br />\n我諗唔到有邊個打得贏佢"},{"pid":"63e9b422b5ec9696d40646c01961245e0ded39ed","tid":795744,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T08:55:50.000Z","msg":"桐人"},{"pid":"558a445883e9151a42d3c7570d4c5eabdf208a59","tid":795744,"uid":79793,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T08:57:37.000Z","msg":"夜神月"},{"pid":"39ff31b50300ff51b382cef97d6e828360e7bdfa","tid":795744,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T08:58:34.000Z","msg":"則卷小雲，無敵於天下"},{"pid":"8780d29ab998c7d3d5d6de8f9617ac3543fb960c","tid":795744,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:00:07.000Z","msg":"講真呢d 純粹鬥大力 既角色根本唔入流<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/165907_7e83e541d848e9a51b29b15ebad5ad3d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F165907_7e83e541d848e9a51b29b15ebad5ad3d.gif&h=1133a6e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高次元既角色 已經操控因果 卒下手指你已經消失"},{"pid":"fb2c3eec8a06a62dad57781c627895b1c827eb56","tid":795744,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:00:24.000Z","msg":"唔好拎套垃圾黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"90fefa4515a531e2ecc578b359f9503f54c5cd26","tid":795744,"uid":759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:00:58.000Z","msg":"拳次郎<br />\n完"},{"pid":"8bd1bc33d24c689ffbb6129bb43b6204497fb1bc","tid":795744,"uid":182314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:01:56.000Z","msg":"天天"},{"pid":"8f5cb376d3ccba4a82360b7cacdf943d4bb62c81","tid":795744,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8780d29ab998c7d3d5d6de8f9617ac3543fb960c","tid":795744,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:00:07.000Z","msg":"講真呢d 純粹鬥大力 既角色根本唔入流<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/165907_7e83e541d848e9a51b29b15ebad5ad3d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F165907_7e83e541d848e9a51b29b15ebad5ad3d.gif&h=1133a6e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高次元既角色 已經操控因果 卒下手指你已經消失"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:02:34.000Z","msg":"咁樣就唔係打贏la ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c7482ff6eb148447416ee835ef45e8545c7314","tid":795744,"uid":33651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:02:55.000Z","msg":"同意樓主，問心果句要打贏本部其實好易<br />\n先唔同其他作品比較，樓主已經比左例子。我從刃牙4部入面分析下。<br />\n本部自己唔算有最勁身體能力 例如刃牙入面都已經有不少人比佢屈機，本部頂多叫「中上」實力，是但第一部搵個人已經贏到佢, 但呢個只局限係「有規則比賽」。<br />\n我諗綜合4部烈海王點都有top5實力<br />\n但點解我認為比唔上本部，係因為佢無「覺悟」，佢無辦法係實戰入面生存。<br />\n烈海王太自負所以先笑本部，最後<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">比武藏斬</span></span>死左。<br />\n無睇既人可以去睇下刃牙，個人認為&gt;拳願<br />\n最後要送上一張圖比大家。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/170029_fce0f4bed909ba9994888a8bfaa1108c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F170029_fce0f4bed909ba9994888a8bfaa1108c.jpg&h=6b3edc78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25dc9d26a29fac9d899f7549c485d09fb4c658ba","tid":795744,"uid":83609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39ff31b50300ff51b382cef97d6e828360e7bdfa","tid":795744,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T08:58:34.000Z","msg":"則卷小雲，無敵於天下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/170307_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F170307_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a0340b8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc2527a41fa53bae067bddb48624c2821b7046f0","tid":795744,"uid":31219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:04:27.000Z","msg":"鳴門？"},{"pid":"58aba01bd0d5e518826aab0b0361bcdb76369f66","tid":795744,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25dc9d26a29fac9d899f7549c485d09fb4c658ba","tid":795744,"uid":83609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39ff31b50300ff51b382cef97d6e828360e7bdfa","tid":795744,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T08:58:34.000Z","msg":"則卷小雲，無敵於天下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/170307_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F170307_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a0340b8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:05:33.000Z","msg":"柒達真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e447f3705adb01ffa83353affccfafac043dcd21","tid":795744,"uid":8307,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"71c7482ff6eb148447416ee835ef45e8545c7314","tid":795744,"uid":33651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:02:55.000Z","msg":"同意樓主，問心果句要打贏本部其實好易<br />\n先唔同其他作品比較，樓主已經比左例子。我從刃牙4部入面分析下。<br />\n本部自己唔算有最勁身體能力 例如刃牙入面都已經有不少人比佢屈機，本部頂多叫「中上」實力，是但第一部搵個人已經贏到佢, 但呢個只局限係「有規則比賽」。<br />\n我諗綜合4部烈海王點都有top5實力<br />\n但點解我認為比唔上本部，係因為佢無「覺悟」，佢無辦法係實戰入面生存。<br />\n烈海王太自負所以先笑本部，最後<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">比武藏斬</span></span>死左。<br />\n無睇既人可以去睇下刃牙，個人認為&gt;拳願<br />\n最後要送上一張圖比大家。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/170029_fce0f4bed909ba9994888a8bfaa1108c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F170029_fce0f4bed909ba9994888a8bfaa1108c.jpg&h=6b3edc78&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:05:56.000Z","msg":"啱,<br />\n可能我講得唔清楚<br />\n依家講多次冇規則限制下同埋肉博打交下<br />\n有邊個打得贏本部?"},{"pid":"e39012bc6ff2325c2a4f979db596906010763578","tid":795744,"uid":189507,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:08:53.000Z","msg":"仲洗講！？梗係琦玉老師啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c03e304194fba52d0db151dad57089b317766a","tid":795744,"uid":8307,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:09:00.000Z","msg":"我諗左咁耐淨係諗到<br />\nmetal gear既big boss或者solid snake有機會同本部打成平手<br />\n樓上啲例子細心諗下都知冇可能打得贏本部<br />\n就算本部讓佢地唔係公園出手,都冇可能贏到"},{"pid":"8e4a2e536ca3b806c91380c8221f469ad780461e","tid":795744,"uid":97439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"千鳥"},{"pid":"740b62f6376e89c306b70c56ac5929143a94213e","tid":795744,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:17:23.000Z","msg":"啱啱突然諗到個人<br />\n呢個世界上應該得羅禮士有機會打得贏本部...<br />\n<br />\nChuck Norris and Superman once fought each other on a bet. The loser had to start wearing his underwear on the outside of his pants.<br />\n羅禮士曾和超人對打，並賭說輸的人要把內褲穿在褲子外面。<br />\n<br />\nSome people wear Superman pajamas. Superman wears Chuck Norris pajamas.<br />\n有些粉絲會穿超人睡衣，超人則穿著羅禮士睡衣。<br />\n<br />\nWhen someone is in trouble it's a job for Superman, when Superman is in trouble it's a job for Chuck Norris.<br />\n普通人發生危難時超人會出動，超人發生危難時羅禮士會出動。<br />\n<br />\nWhen Batman is in trouble, he turns on the Chuck Norris signal.<br />\n當蝙蝠俠遇到問題，他會用探照燈打出羅禮士的頭像。<br />\n<br />\nChuck Norris once urinated in a semi truck's gas tank as a joke... that truck is now known as Optimus Prime.<br />\n有一次羅禮士惡作劇尿在一輛貨櫃車的油箱裏... 那輛車後來變成我們知道的「變形金剛」柯博文。"},{"pid":"fde59d808e7f43beaf3460bb92c2b8bd087b9d86","tid":795744,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:36:03.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"d95dca70e7acfc2f2bde503c952a2459e3f2437a","tid":795744,"uid":26031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:48:24.000Z","msg":"咩武術都識但淨係唔識相撲手隻尾指咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f8d7954b0bc436fce2f0056da3fb85d48c3360","tid":795744,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:04:45.000Z","msg":"藍柒"},{"pid":"99d24a6e024d72aa49507fbccc85af1ce0a23f13","tid":795744,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:52:10.000Z","msg":"大岡"},{"pid":"6335327231f38820c2e454f9e691bb69119e6ffe","tid":795744,"uid":81192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T12:00:51.000Z","msg":"令狐沖呢"},{"pid":"5f05f06b2dff558c376081db32c9b0ef5db784fd","tid":795744,"uid":132264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:36:10.000Z","msg":"大雄唔係公園應該有得打"},{"pid":"37fffddf343319000d8f32ca93005891f8fb406c","tid":795744,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:38:23.000Z","msg":"行運超人"}]}